Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20these%20things%20led%20to%20misunderstandings%2C%20which%20led%20the%20kids%20to%20say%20things%20like%20%26quot%3BI%20hate%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BYou're%20the%20worst%20dad%20ever%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BI%20never%20want%20to%20talk%20to%20you%20again.%26quot%3B%3Cspan%3E%20They%20often%20wondered%20why%20I%20couldn't%20be%20as%20%26quot%3Bcool%20as%20the%20other%20dads.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20words%20cut%20to%20the%20core%2C%20and%20I%20remember%20never%20feeling%20appreciated%20for%20my%20efforts%20as%20a%20father.%20It%20always%20seemed%20like%20my%20teenagers%20had%20a%20pattern%3B%20if%20they%20were%20belligerent%2C%20something%20was%20going%20on%20with%20their%20friends%2C%20and%20I%20let%20them%20get%20away%20with%20a%20little%20bit%20more.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20they%20were%20obedient%2C%20I%20knew%20they%20were%20guilty%20of%20something%2C%20and%20I%20would%20tighten%20the%20reins.%20The%20constant%20%26quot%3Bcatch%20me%20if%20you%20can%26quot%3B%20game%20made%20parenting%20feel%20personal.%20I%20had%20many%20moments%20of%20self-doubt%20when%20I%20wondered%20whether%20I%20was%20really%20doing%20a%20good%20job.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20wife%20and%20I%20would%20constantly%20remind%20each%20other%20that%20we%20were%20indeed%20doing%20our%20best%2C%20especially%20when%20we%20wanted%20to%20connect%20with%20the%20kids%2C%20but%20they%20built%20walls%20we%20couldn't%20reach.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20painful%20memory%20comes%20to%20mind%2C%20when%20my%20daughters%20required%20being%20dropped%20off%20a%20block%20away%20from%20school.%20They%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20they%20did%20not%20want%20anyone%20seeing%20their%20dad%20because%20I%20embarrassed%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20especially%20disappointing%20because%20I%20cherished%20the%20drive%20to%20school.%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20