s%20by%20quickly%20for%20all%20of%20us%20or%20gain%20an%20appreciation%20for%20their%20parents.%20My%20love%20for%20them%20has%20never%20faltered%20despite%20all%20the%20trying%20times.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fraising-teenagers-felt-personal-but-i-learnt-to-dig-deeper-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739308262000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a64f3eeb4be2fff9a3f580%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fraising-teenagers-felt-personal-but-i-learnt-to-dig-deeper-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20was%20not%20prepared%20for%20how%20hard%20it%20was%20going%20to%20be%20to%20parent%20teenagers.%20They%20would%20fight%20my%20rules%20and%20tell%20me%20they%20hated%20me.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Tim%20Stevensen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fraising-teenagers-felt-personal-but-i-learnt-to-dig-deeper-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Professional%20cleaners%20share%206%20red%20flags%20they'd%20look%20for%20when%20hiring%20someone%20to%20clean%20a%20home%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226240%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Person%20cleaning%20rug%20with%20vacuum%20tool%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679cf4c57bb3f854015b532f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhen%20hiring%20someone%20to%20clean%20your%20house%2C%20you'll%20want%20to%20look%20out%20for%20a%20few%20possible%20red%20flags.%3Cp%3ESergio%20Mendoza%20Hochmann%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20asked%20professional%20cleaners%20about%20red%20flags%20they'd%20look%20for%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhaving-cleaning-person-takes-up-budget-but-its-worth-it-2022-4%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehiring%20someone%20to%20clean%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20home.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESuspiciously%20low%20cleaning%20prices%20might%20draw%20you%20in%2C%20but%20you%20could%20get%20hit%20with%20surprise%20fees%20later.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIf%20cleaners%20don't%20offer%20walkthroughs%20after%20a%20service%2C%20they%20may%20not%20stand%20behind%20their%20work.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20people%20hire%20professional%20house%20cleaners%20to%20help%20keep%20their%20homes%20looking%20good%20on%20a%20weekly%2C%20biweekly%2C%20or%20monthly%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20trying%20to%20decide%20who%20to%20bring%20into%20your%20home%2C%20reading%20online%20reviews%20is%20a%20good%20place%20to%20start.%20Still%2C%20there%20are%20a%20few%20other%20things%20you%20may%20want%20to%20look%20for%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcleaning-expert-five-mistakes-people-make-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehiring%20a%20cleaning%20service%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20Business%20Insider%20asked%20professional%20cleaners%20about%20the%20red%20flags%20they%20would%20look%20for%20when%20hiring%20someone.%20Here's%20what%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2209d78c71-3794-4a34-babb-157637ceadee%5C%22%3EThere's%20no%20satisfaction%20guarantee%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlways%20look%20for%20cleaners%20or%20cleaning%20companies%20that%20stand%20behind%20their%20work%20by%20offering%20some%20kind%20of%20satisfaction%20guarantee%2C%20said%20Robin%20Murphy%2C%20founder%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chirpchirp.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChirpChirp%20House%20Cleaning%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20good%20sign%20when%20cleaning%20companies%20offer%20to%20come%20back%20or%20redo%20a%20service%20if%20customers%20are%20not%20satisfied.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Murphy%20said%20she'd%20look%20for%20stronger%20guarantees%2C%20such%20as%20refunds%20or%20no-charge%20reworks%2C%20as%20these%20claims%20can%20demonstrate%20a%20company's%20confidence%20and%20commitment%20to%20its%20cleaning%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d4346c04-57ce-4f2e-973f-db52a7eef9a5%5C%22%3EPrices%20feel%20suspiciously%20low%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20looking%20for%20a%20cleaning%20service%2C%20it's%20wise%20to%20research%20average%20prices%20in%20your%20local%20area%20to%20learn%20what%20to%20expect.%20If%20you%20find%20a%20company%20offering%20a%20low%20price%20that%20seems%20too%20good%20to%20be%20true%2C%20it%20probably%20is%2C%20Murphy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20told%20BI%20that%20some%20companies%20price%20their%20services%20low%20on%20purpose%20to%20lure%20in%20customers%20only%20to%20later%20hit%20them%20with%20hidden%20fees%20and%20%26quot%3Bimpose%20additional%20charges.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20in%20doubt%2C%20ask%20what%20is%20included%20in%20the%20price%20of%20a%20clean%20and%20what%20costs%20extra%20%E2%80%94%20and%20always%20read%20the%20fine%20print%20of%20a%20contract.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2299401eee-264e-4b0b-8f64-b7aeb57b083c%5C%22%3ETools%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20the%20cleaning%20rags%20%E2%80%94%20appear%20unclean%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228256%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Person%20with%20gloves%20on%20wiping%20down%20a%20shelf%20with%20microfiber%20cloth%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679cf5cc7bb3f854015b5361%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECleaning%20companies%20that%20have%20no%20satisfaction%20guarantees%20may%20not%20stand%20behind%20their%20work.%3Cp%3EArtistGNDphotography%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERhonda%20Wilson%2C%20lead%20cleaner%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffreshspacecleaning.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFreshSpace%20Cleaning%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20people%20should%20pay%20attention%20to%20cleaners'%20rags%20and%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20your%20cleaner%20brings%20in%20old%2C%20worn-out%20rags%20and%20dirty%20equipment%2C%20that%20is%20a%20big%20red%20flag%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilson%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20our%20profession%2C%20we're%20expected%20to%20have%20batches%20of%20clean%2C%20absorbent%20microfiber%20cloths%20and%20clean%20our%20tools%20every%20after%20a%20cleaning%20appointment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilson%20added%20that%20dirty%20supplies%20can%20spread%20grime%20around%20surfaces%20rather%20than%20cleaning%20them%20or%20even%20cause%20cross-contamination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229a7bb5f9-f7a4-4b34-837b-71593ea14dbc%5C%22%3EThe%20cleaner%20doesn't%20ask%20for%20or%20ignores%20instructions%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20people%20hire%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-best-money-i-ever-spent-was-on-a-housekeeper-2015-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecleaners%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it's%20not%20uncommon%20to%20provide%20them%20with%20instructions%20about%20what%20they're%20looking%20for%20or%20which%20items%20in%20the%20home%20to%20be%20careful%20with%20or%20avoid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20Wilson%20said%2C%20it's%20a%20huge%20red%20flag%20if%20a%20cleaner%20doesn't%20ask%20for%20preferences%20or%20ignores%20your%20instructions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20good%20cleaner%20should%20be%20a%20good%20listener%20and%20follower.%20If%20they're%20willing%20to%20tweak%20their%20methods%20and%20products%20based%20on%20your%20feedback%2C%20then%20you%20found%20a%20great%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ad31d51a-df35-47ea-9ff9-9c428a48be89%5C%22%3EThey%20don't%20offer%20to%20do%20a%20walkthrough%20after%20a%20service%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20sign%20of%20good%20service%20when%20cleaners%20offer%20to%20conduct%20walkthroughs%2C%20and%20may%20even%20be%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20red%20flag%20if%20they