articleshow%2F118156314.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kanye%20West's%204%20days%20of%20controversy%3A%20a%20Super%20Bowl%20ad%2C%20a%20swastika%20T-shirt%2C%20and%20a%20Shopify%20shutdown%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224349%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kanye%20West%2C%20or%20Ye%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ab7f377bb3f854015c7c2e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223262%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKanye%20West%2C%20legally%20known%20as%20Ye%2C%20had%20his%20online%20store%20shut%20down%20by%20Shopify.%3Cp%3EMatt%20Winkelmeyer%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20The%20Recording%20Academy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EKanye%20West's%20Super%20Bowl%20ad%20pointed%20people%20to%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FYEEZY.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYEEZY.com%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20was%20later%20updated%20to%20feature%20only%20a%20swastika%20T-shirt.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAfter%20the%20listing%20received%20backlash%2C%20Shopify%20removed%20the%20website%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShopify%20has%20faced%20criticism%20before%20for%20hosting%20controversial%20stores%2C%20leading%20to%20policy%20changes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFour%20days%20of%20Kanye%20West%20controversy%20came%20to%20a%20head%20on%20Tuesday%20when%20the%20artist's%20website%20was%20taken%20offline%20after%20facing%20backlash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20website%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewas%20removed%20by%20the%20vendor%20powering%20it%2C%20Shopify%2C%20less%20than%2048%20hours%20after%20West's%20Super%20Bowl%20ad%20directed%20viewers%20to%20a%20storefront%20selling%20a%20single%20item%3A%20a%20swastika%20T-shirt%20labeled%20%26quot%3BHH-01.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Shopify%20spokesperson%20confirmed%20to%20BI%20on%20Tuesday%20morning%20the%20company%20had%20removed%20the%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20merchants%20are%20responsible%20for%20following%20the%20rules%20of%20our%20platform.%20This%20merchant%20did%20not%20engage%20in%20authentic%20commerce%20practices%20and%20violated%20our%20terms%20so%20we%20removed%20them%20from%20Shopify%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20West%2C%20whose%20legal%20name%20is%20Ye%2C%20posted%20a%20slew%20of%20social%20media%20posts%20on%20X%20praising%20Adolf%20Hitler%2C%20describing%20himself%20as%20a%20Nazi%2C%20and%20defending%20music%20mogul%20Sean%20%26quot%3BDiddy%26quot%3B%20Combs%2C%20who%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsean-diddy-combs-arrested-grand-jury-indictment-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earrested%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20September%20and%20charged%20with%20racketeering%20conspiracy%2C%20sex%20trafficking%2C%20and%20transportation%20to%20engage%20in%20prostitution.%20Combs%20has%20pleaded%20not%20guilty%20to%20the%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYe%20also%20purchased%20a%2030-second%20ad%20that%20aired%20during%20Super%20Bowl%20LIX.%20Unlike%20the%20national%20Super%20Bowl%20ads%20that%20reached%20a%20cost%20of%20north%20of%20%248%20million%20for%2030%20seconds%20of%20airtime%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Yeezy%20team%20instead%20purchased%20ad%20slots%20on%20local%20stations%20%E2%80%94%20which%20would%20have%20come%20at%20a%20lower%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ads%20ran%20on%20local%20Fox%20stations%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20Philadelphia%2C%20and%20Atlanta%2C%20and%20some%20other%20affiliate%20stations%2C%20according%20to%20USIM%2C%20the%20media%20agency%20that%20brokered%20the%20buy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDoug%20Livingston%2C%20president%20and%20chief%20operating%20officer%20of%20USIM%2C%20said%20the%20agency%20immediately%20ceased%20working%20with%20Yeezy%20LLC%20after%20seeing%20the%20%26quot%3Bdisparaging%20and%20vile%20comments%26quot%3B%20Ye%20had%20posted%20on%20X%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELivingston%20said%20Fox%20had%20said%20the%20media%20buy%20was%20%26quot%3Bnon-cancelable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20informed%20Fox%20that%20they%20should%20cease%20airing%20any%20remnant%20spots%20immediately%20upon%20learning%20that%20Yeezy%2C%20LLC%20was%20promoting%20vile%20content%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Fox%20insider%20told%20BI%20they%20received%20no%20communication%20from%20the%20agency%20about%20requesting%20to%20drop%20the%20ad%20until%20Monday%20morning%20after%20the%20Super%20Bowl%20spot%20had%20aired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Yeezy%20Super%20Bowl%20spot%2C%20which%20purported%20to%20be%20shot%20on%20an%20iPhone%20and%20featured%20the%20rapper%20sitting%20in%20a%20dentist's%20chair%20showing%20off%20his%20new%20teeth%2C%20was%20unlikely%20to%20have%20caused%20alarm%20when%20it%20was%20submitted%20and%20subsequently%20approved%20for%20broadcast%20because%20it%20didn't%20contain%20any%20obscenities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20whassup%20guys%2C%20I%20spent%20like%20all%20the%20money%20for%20the%20commercial%20on%20these%20new%20teeth.%20So%2C%20once%20again%20I%20had%20to%20shoot%20it%20on%20the%20iPhone.%20Um%2C%20um%2C%20um%2C%20go%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FYeezy.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYeezy.com%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20Ye%20said%20in%20the%20sparse%20ad.%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FYeezy.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYeezy.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20ran%20a%20local%20spot%20during%20last%20year's%20Super%20Bowl%2C%20starring%20Ye.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%20of%20the%20ad's%20approval%20and%20airing%2C%20the%20Yeezy%20store%20displayed%20a%20number%20of%20items%20for%20sale.%20It%20was%20only%20after%20the%20ad%20was%20shown%20that%20the%20website%20was%20updated%20to%20display%20the%20swastika%20T-shirt%20for%20sale%2C%20according%20to%20screenshots%20of%20the%20site%20captured%20by%20the%20Internet%20Archive's%20Wayback%20Machine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUSIM's%20Livingston%20said%20the%20agency%20was%20unaware%20that%20Ye%20had%20intended%20to%20change%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20store's%20offerings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20commercial%20was%20to%20promote%20general%20athletic%20apparel%20listed%20on%20the%20website%2C%26quot%3B%20Livingston%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20his%20website%2C%20Ye's%20X%20account%20appears%20to%20also%20be%20deactivated%20on%20the%20platform%20as%20of%20Tuesday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYe%20is%20an%20intergenerational%20artist%20and%20icon%20who%20continues%20to%20redefine%20the%20limits%20of%20creativity%20and%20free%20expression.%20He%20has%20deactivated%20his%20X%20account%20for%20the%20time%20being%2C%26quot%3B%20spokesperson%20Milo%20Yiannopoulos%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FNero%2Fstatus%2F1889255545128857863%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20NBC%20News.%20Representatives%20for%20Ye%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20further%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYe%20was%20previously%20banned%20from%20X%2C%20then%20known%20as%20Twitter%2C%20in%202022%20after%20he%20tweeted%20an%20image%20containing%20a%20swastika%20and%20the%20Star%20of%20David.%20His%20account%20was%20later%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmusk-reinstates-kanye-wests-twitter-x-account-after-ban-antisemitism-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereinstated%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20hours%20following%20the%20Super%20Bowl%20ad%20airing%2C%20many%20called%20for%20the%20Yeezy%20site%20to%20be%20taken%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20week%2C%20the%20Anti-Defamation%20League%2C%20which%20called%20the%20T-shirt%20listing%20%26quot%3Bfurther%20proof%20of%20Kanye's%20antisemitism%2C%26quot%3B%20encouraged%20people%20to%20sign%20an%20open%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faction.adl.org%2Fa%2Fkanye-super-bowl%3Fsourceid%3D1082070%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eletter%3C%2Fa%3E%20calling%20on%20F