t's%202025%2C%20and%20the%20person%20making%20the%20offer%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E.%20So%20that's%20a%20very%20appropriate%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20deal%20in%20question%3A%20A%20%2497.375%20billion%20offer%20from%20a%20consortium%2C%20led%20by%20the%20world's%20richest%20man%2C%20to%20buy%20at%20least%20part%20of%20OpenAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mechanics%20of%20this%20theoretical%20deal%20get%20complicated%20pretty%20quickly%2C%20since%20OpenAi%20is%20a%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fopenai%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ecomplicated%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20organization.%20As%20is%20often%20the%20case%2C%20Matt%20Levine%20at%20Bloomberg%20has%20a%20very%20useful%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fopinion%2Farticles%2F2025-02-11%2Fsure-elon-musk-might-buy-openai%3Fsrnd%3Dundefined%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexplainer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20it%20boils%20down%20to%20this%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ERight%20now%2C%20OpenAI%20is%20a%20nonprofit%20organization%20that%20controls%20a%20very%20valuable%20business.%20It's%20the%20group%20that%20created%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-chat-gpt-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20other%20AI%20properties%2C%20and%20it%20has%20even%20grander%20plans.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOpenAI%20leader%20Sam%20Altman%20wants%20to%20convert%20OpenAI%20into%20a%20for-profit%20business%2C%20and%20plans%20on%20giving%20the%20nonprofit%20part%20of%20OpenAI%20a%20stake%20in%20the%20for-profit%20business.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMusk%20and%20his%20theoretical%20co-investors%20argue%20that%20this%20is%20a%20sweetheart%20deal%20that%20will%20short-change%20OpenAI%2C%20the%20nonprofit%20company.%20So%20they're%20offering%20to%20buy%20the%20nonprofit%20part%20of%20OpenAI%20for%20%26quot%3Bno%20less%20than%20%2497.375%20billion%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20a%20letter%20from%20Marc%20Toberoff%2C%20an%20attorney%20representing%20the%20Musk%20coalition.%20(I've%20asked%20both%20Toberoff%20and%20OpenAI%20for%20comment.)%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20have%20to%20summarize%20something%20with%20three%20bullet%20points%2C%20it's%20already%20pretty%20complicated.%20But%20it%20gets%20more%20complicated%20from%20here%2C%20because%20now%20we%20have%20to%20guess%20at%20whether%20Musk%20actually%20plans%20on%20doing%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20conventional%20wisdom%2C%20which%20quickly%20coalesced%20after%20Musk%20made%20his%20offer%20on%20Monday%2C%20is%20no.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20argument%20mainly%20hinges%20on%20the%20idea%20that%20Musk%20is%20simply%20trying%20to%20jam%20up%20Altman%2C%20his%20former%20ally-turned-rival.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Ftech%2Fai%2Fmusks-97-4-billion-openai-bid-piles-pressure-on-altman-f6749e6c%3Fmod%3Dhp_lead_pos1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enotes%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%26quot%3BMusk's%20offer%20could%20force%20OpenAI's%20board%20of%20directors%20to%20reassess%20how%20it%20is%20valuing%20the%20nonprofit%2C%20which%20the%20board%20has%20said%20will%20be%20fairly%20compensated%20in%20the%20transaction%20and%20own%20a%20stake%20in%20the%20for-profit.%20The%20higher%20the%20valuation%20of%20the%20nonprofit%2C%20the%20bigger%20its%20stake%20would%20likely%20be%20in%20the%20for-profit%20OpenAI%20following%20a%20conversion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20will%20further%20complicate%20a%20giant%20funding%20deal%20that%20was%20supposed%20to%20value%20OpenAI%20at%20%24300%20billion%3B%20if%20Musk's%20offer%20raises%20the%20value%20of%20the%20non-profit%20part%20of%20OpenAI%2C%20it%20changes%20the%20calculations%20for%20investors%20in%20the%20for-profit%20part%20of%20OpenAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOr%2C%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-elon-musk-openai-bid-insecure-rivalry-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAltman's%20words%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20he%20is%20probably%20just%20trying%20to%20slow%20us%20down.%20He%20obviously%20is%20a%20competitor.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20there%20are%20other%20reasons%20to%20raise%20at%20least%20one%20eyebrow%20at%20Musk's%20offer.%20The%20first%20is%20Musk's%20affinity%20for%20saying%20one%20thing%20and%20doing%20another.%20Like%20last%20March%2C%20when%20he%20wrote%20that%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20donating%20money%20to%20either%20candidate%20for%20US%20President%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20and%20then%20went%20on%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-260-million-spending-trump-republican-party-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edonate%20more%20than%20a%20quarter%20of%20a%20billion%20dollars%20to%20Donald%20Trump's%20presidential%20campaign%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20specifically%2C%20Musk%20has%20previously%20floated%20deals%20that%20either%20aren't%20real%20or%20that%20he%20tried%20to%20back%20out%20of.%20Like%20in%202018%2C%20when%20he%20said%20he%20had%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Flegal%2Fsecurities-fraud-trial-over-elon-musks-2018-tweets-draws-close-2023-02-03%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efunding%20secured%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20to%20take%20Tesla%20private%2C%20but%20he%20didn't%20have%20funding%20secured%2C%20and%20he%20didn't%20take%20Tesla%20private.%20Or%20in%202022%2C%20when%20he%20signed%20a%20fast-tracked%20deal%20to%20buy%20Twitter%20and%20take%20it%20private%20%E2%80%94%20and%20then%20spent%20weeks%20trying%20to%20void%20the%20deal%2C%20saying%20that%20he'd%20been%20deceived%20by%20Twitter's%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20flip%20version%20of%20that%20argument%20is%20that%20betting%20against%20Elon%20Musk%20doing%20something%20is%20a%20very%20