pplebee's%20in%20April%20showed%20that%2064%25%20of%20its%20guests%20were%20interested%20in%20or%20very%20interested%20in%20the%20NFL%2C%20and%20around%2034%25%20had%20watched%20the%20NFL%20in%20the%20past%20year%2C%20which%20helped%20shape%20the%20chain's%20strategy%20for%20the%20football%20season%2C%20Yashinsky%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20cheeseburger%20came%20with%20two%20slices%20of%20American%20cheese%2C%20lettuce%2C%20tomato%2C%20red%20onion%2C%20and%20pickles%20on%20a%20brioche%20bun.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22applebees%20cheeseburger%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ab901aeb4be2fff9a4449c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20burger%20was%20cooked%20perfectly%20medium-rare.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20burger%20patty's%20exterior%20was%20noticeably%20dark%2C%20initially%20making%20me%20worry%20that%20it%20had%20been%20overcooked%20beyond%20the%20medium%20level%20I%20had%20requested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20to%20my%20surprise%2C%20it%20was%20incredibly%20juicy%20and%20even%20leaned%20slightly%20toward%20medium-rare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20melted%2C%20tangy%20cheese%20covered%20the%20entire%20burger%2C%20creating%20a%20perfectly%20balanced%20bite.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22applebees%20cheeseburger%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67990d7beb4be2fff9a26e2c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20thought%20the%20toppings%20tasted%20fresh.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20thick%20slices%20of%20red%20onion%20added%20a%20lot%20of%20bold%2C%20tangy%20flavor%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20delightful%20amount%20of%20crunch%20to%20each%20bite.%20I%20also%20thought%20the%20lettuce%20and%20tomato%20slices%20tasted%20fresh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20this%20burger%20didn't%20come%20with%20any%20sauce%2C%20it%20was%20still%20moist%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20melted%20cheese%20and%20a%20buttery%20bun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Applebee's%20burger%20was%20slightly%20topped%20by%20the%20burger%20from%20Buffalo%20Wild%20Wings.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22buffalo%20wild%20wings%20all%20american%20cheeseburger%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ab90b47bb3f854015c82a7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20burger%20came%20with%20two%20burger%20patties%20sandwiched%20between%20a%20soft%20bun.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ordered%20the%20All-American%20Cheeseburger%20at%20my%20local%20Buffalo%20Wild%20Wings%20in%20Brooklyn%2C%20New%20York.%20It%20cost%20%2414.49%2C%20excluding%20tax.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20typically%20regard%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freview-is-buffalo-wild-wings-worth-it-for-family-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBuffalo%20Wild%20Wings%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20chicken%20chain%2C%20known%20for%20its%20traditional%20and%20boneless%20wings%2C%20so%20I%20was%20surprised%20by%20how%20much%20I%20enjoyed%20this%20classic%20cheeseburger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20burger%20came%20with%20two%20beef%20patties%20instead%20of%20one%2C%20even%20though%20it%20was%20less%20expensive%20than%20Applebee's.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22buffalo%20wild%20wings%20all%20american%20cheeseburger%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ab90c9eb4be2fff9a44513%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20burger%20came%20coated%20in%20layers%20of%20melted%20cheese.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2