n%20equal%20opportunity%20sexual%20predator.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20October%20lawsuit%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmacys-covered-up-2008-flagship-store-sex-attack-diddy-lawsuit-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccuses%20Macy's%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20violating%20a%20New%20York%20City%20gender-violence%20law%20by%20covering%20up%20an%20alleged%20attack%20by%20Combs%20on%20a%20male%20employee%20at%20the%20Herald%20Square%20flagship%20store%20in%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20worldwide%20department%20chain%20argues%20the%20plaintiff%2C%20only%20identified%20as%20John%20Doe%2C%20cannot%20accuse%20Macy's%20of%20gender%20bias%20because%2C%20in%20the%20very%20same%20lawsuit%2C%20Doe%20himself%20describes%20Combs%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdiddys-career-life-fell-apart-one-year-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewilling%20to%20attack%20both%20men%20and%20women%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlaintiff's%20own%20allegations%20establish%20not%20only%20that%20this%20was%20a%20same-sex%20assault%2C%20but%20that%20Mr.%20Combs%20sexually%20assaulted%20both%20men%20and%20women%2C%20without%20regard%20to%20gender%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Macy's%20lawyers%20argued%20in%20court%20papers%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlaintiff%20does%20not%20address%20the%20fact%20that%20his%20own%20allegations%20establish%20that%20Mr.%20Combs%20was%20an%20equal%20opportunity%20sexual%20predator.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Combs%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20Macy's%20argument.%20Combs%20has%20repeatedly%20denied%20any%20sexual%20assaults.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDistrict%20Court%20Judge%20J.%20Paul%20Oetken's%20decision%20on%20whether%20to%20dismiss%20Macy's%20could%20come%20at%20any%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMacy's%20is%20the%20deepest-pocket%20defendant%20by%20far%20in%20any%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdiddy-lawsuits-celebrities-list%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20blizzard%20of%20more%20than%2030%20sex-assault%20lawsuits%3C%2Fa%3E%20filed%20against%20the%20rapper%20in%20the%20past%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plaintiff%20says%20in%20his%20lawsuit%20that%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20alleged%20attack%2C%20he%20was%20working%20at%20Macy's%20flagship%20Manhattan%20store%20for%20Ecko%2C%20a%20rival%20hip-hop%20fashion%20brand%20to%20Combs'%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdiddy-earnings-net-worth-billionaire-hip-hops-richest-business-men-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESean%20John%20Clothing.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F25204963-combs-lawsuit-macys-attack-complaint-20241014%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EHis%2019-page%20lawsuit%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20alleges%20that%20he%20was%20working%20in%20a%20stockroom%20when%20Combs%20entered%20with%20three%20armed%20bodyguards%20who%20struck%20him%20and%20threatened%20to%20kill%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECombs%20then%20orally%20raped%20him%20in%20the%20stockroom%2C%20while%20calling%20him%20%26quot%3BEcko%26quot%3B%20and%20taunting%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20like%20that%2C%20white%20boy%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20alleges.%20After%20what%20was%20alleged%20to%20be%20a%20two-minute%20attack%2C%20Combs%20then%20grabbed%20armfuls%20of%20Sean%20Jean%20clothing%2C%20left%20the%20stockroom%20with%20his%20bodyguards%2C%20and%20proceeded%20to%20hand%20out%20clothes%20to%20shoppers%20%26quot%3Bas%20if%20nothing%20had%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plaintiff%20alleges%20that%20the%20chain%20did%20nothing%20to%20support%20him%20when%20he%20came%20forward%20with%20his%20allegations%20against%20Combs%2C%20and%20instead%20fired%20him%20to%20protect%20a%20multimillion-dollar%20deal%20with%20Sean%20Jean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fighting%20to%20be%20dropped%20as%20a%20defendant%2C%20lawyers%20for%20Macy's%20argued%20that%20the%20lawsuit%20does%20not%20allege%20store%20employees%20were%20in%20any%20way%20involved%20in%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMacy's%20lawyers%20also%20pointed%20to%20the%20New%20York%20City%20Victims%20of%20Gender-Motivated%20Violence%20Protection%20Law.%20The%20lawyers%20for%20the%20man%20had%20argued%20in%20their%20lawsuit%20that%20the%20gender%20violence%20law%20entitled%20their%20client%20to%20seek%20damages%20from%20Macy's.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMacy's%20countered%20that%20the%20law%20does%20not%20permit%20claims%20against%20corporations%20for%20assaults%20prior%20to%202022%2C%20and%20that%20the%20lawsuit%20failed%20to%20offer%20any%20evidence%20that%20the%20alleged%20violence%20was%20motivated%20by%20gender%20bias.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECombs'%20alleged%20%26quot%3Bwhite%20boy%26quot%3B%20taunt%20does%20not%20refer%20to%20gender%20bias%2C%20Macy's%20lawyers%20argued%20in%20papers%20signed%20by%20attorney%20Daniel%20Kotler.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20word%20%26quot%3Bboy%26quot%3B%20in%20that%20scenario%20%26quot%3Bfunctions%20primarily%20as%20a%20term%20of%20status%20and%20belittlement%20(boy%20versus%20man)%20rather%20than%20as%20a%20gendered%20comment%20(boy%20versus%20girl)%20%E2%80%94%20it%20is%20in%20effect%20an%20inversion%20of%20the%20classically%20racist%20use%20of%20the%20term%20'boy'%20to%20degrade%20or%20belittle%20African%20Americans%2C%26quot%3B%20Macy's%20side%20argued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKotler%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20for%20this%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuzbee%2C%20the%20lead%20attorney%20for%20the%20plaintiff%2C%20counters%20in%20court%20papers%20that%20the%20New%20York%20gender-violence%20law%20does%20cover%20corporations%20involved%20in%20attacks%20prior%20to%202022.%20He%20also%20argues%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20fact%20that%20Combs%20violently%20assaulted%20people%20of%20both%20genders%20does%20not%20somehow%20exempt%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehim%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20pretty%20novel%20argument%20that%20should%20fail%2C%26quot%3B%20Buzbee%20told%20Business%20Insider%20on%20Tuesday%20of%20Macy's%20dismissal%20arguments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmacys-wants-to-be-dropped-from-diddy-sex-lawsuit-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739303913000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ab6b7e7bb3f854015c76d2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmacys-wants-to-be-dropped-from-diddy-sex-lawsuit-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lawyers%20for%20Macy's%20call%20Combs%20%26quot%3Ban%20equal%20opportunity%20sexual%20predator%26quot%3B%20in%20arguing%20that%20the%20male%20accuser%20therefore%20can't%20sue%20for%20gender-based%20violence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22litaliano%40insider.com%20(Laura%20Italiano)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A34%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmacys-wants-to-be-dropped-from-diddy-sex-lawsuit-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20Pauses%20Anti-Bribery%20Law%3A%20What%20It%20Means%20For%20Adani%20Group%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20ordered%20a%20pause%20in%20the%20enforcement%20of%20a%20nearly%20half-century-old%20law%20that%20was%20used%20to%20go%20after%20the%20Adani%20Group%20under%20the%20previous%20Biden%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Foreign%20Corrupt%20Practices%20Act%20(FCPA)%20bans%20firms%20and%20people%20with%20US%20ties%20from%20offering%20money%20or%20gifts%20to%20foreign%20officials%20to%20secure%20business%20overseas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Trump%20had%20considered%20pausing%20the%20law%20during%20his%20first%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20sounds%20good%20on%20paper%2C%20but%20in%20%5Bpractice%5D%20it's%20a%20disaster%2C%26quot%3B%20President%20Trump%20said%20on%20the%20FCPA%2C%20the%20British%20daily%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2Ff880bfc3-6069-427b-9873-51255d4e0b8c%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20%26quot%3BIt%20means%20that%20if%20an%20American%20goes%20over%20to%20a%20foreign%20country%20and%20starts%20doing%20business%20over%20there%20legally%2C%20legitimately%20or%20otherwise%2C%20it's%20almost%20a%20guaranteed%20investigation%2C%20indictment%20and%20nobody%20wants%20to%20do%20business%20with%20the%20Americans%20because%20of%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20marks%20one%20of%20the%20boldest%20enforcement%20policies%20issued%20by%20the%20Trump%20administration%2C%20FT%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20-%20the%20largest%20and%20fastest-growing%20portfolio%20of%20diversified%20businesses%20in%20India%20-%20last%20year%20strongly%20denied%20allegations%20by%20the%20Biden%20administration%20that%20some%20company%20officials%20were%20part%20of%20an%20alleged%20scheme%20to%20pay%20over%20%24250%20million%20bribe%20to%20Indian%20officials%20in%20exchange%20for%20favourable%20terms%20for%20solar%20power%20contracts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20Over-expansive%20and%20unpredictable%20FCPA%20enforcement%20against%20American%20citizens%20and%20businesses%20-%20by%20our%20own%20Government%20-%20for%20routine%20business%20practices%20in%20other%20nations%20not%20only%20wastes%20limited%20prosecutorial%20resources%20that%20could%20be%20dedicated%20to%20preserving%20American%20freedoms%2C%20but%20actively%20harms%20American%20economic%20competitiveness%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20national%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20White%20House%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20pausing%20the%20FCPA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20therefore%20the%20policy%20of%20my%20Administration%20to%20preserve%20the%20Presidential%20authority%20to%20conduct%20foreign%20affairs%20and%20advance%20American%20economic%20and%20national%20security%20by%20eliminating%20excessive%20barriers%20to%20American%20commerce%20abroad%2C%26quot%3B%20President%20Trump's%20executive%20order%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fop19b72o_adani-generic_625x300_05_August_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20executive%20order%20that%20President%20Trump%20signed%20asked%20the%20US%20Attorney%20General%20to%20%26quot%3Breview%20in%20detail%20all%20existing%20FCPA%20investigations%20or%20enforcement%20actions%20and%20take%20appropriate%20action%20with%20respect%20to%20such%20matters%20to%20restore%20proper%20bounds%20on%20FCPA%20enforcement%20and%20preserve%20Presidential%20foreign%20policy%20prerogatives%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20executive%20order%20to%20pause%20the%20enforcement%20of%20the%20FCPA%2C%20stocks%20of%20all%20Adani%20Group%20firms%20saw%20substantial%20gains%20today.%20The%20most%20notable%20gainer%20was%20Adani%20Enterprises%20Ltd%2C%20whose%20stock%20rose%204.28%20per%20cent.%20Following%20closely%20was%20Adani%20Power%20Ltd%2C%20which%20rose%204.17%20per%20cent%20to%20Rs%20511.90%20apiece.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20Green%20Energy%20Ltd%20was%20the%20third%20top%20gainer%2C%20as%20it%20rose%203.34%20per%20cent%20to%20Rs%20985.90%20apiece.%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20Ltd%20(NDTV)%20stock%20rose%203.84%20per%20cent%20to%20Rs%20145%20apiece.%20The%20shares%20of%20Adani%20Energy%20Solutions%20Ltd%2C%20Adani%20Total%20Gas%20Ltd%2C%20and%20Adani%20Ports%20and%20Special%20Economic%20Zone%20Ltd%20also%20saw%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20six%20US%20Congressmen%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20Attorney%20General%20Pam%20Bondi%20said%20the%20previous%20Department%20of%20Justice's%20(DoJ)%20action%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bmisguided%20crusade%26quot%3B%20that%20came%20at%20the%20%26quot%3Brisk%20of%20harming%26quot%3B%20America's%20relationship%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bstrategic%20geopolitical%20partner%26quot%3B%20like%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20called%20it%20one%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bunwise%20decisions%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20Biden%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20case%20rests%20on%20the%20allegation%20that%20preparations%20were%20made%20by%20members%20of%20this%20company%20in%20India%20to%20bribe%20Indian%20officials%2C%20also%20exclusively%20located%20in%20India.%20Instead%20of%20deferring%20the%20case%20to%20the%20appropriate%20Indian%20authorities%2C%20the%20Biden%20DoJ%20decided%20to%20push%20forward%20and%20indict%20the%20company's%20executives%20without%20any%20real%20injury%20to%20US%20interests%20being%20present%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20six%20Congressmen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20has%20interests%20in%20logistics%20(seaports%2C%20airports%2C%20logistics%2C%20shipping%20and%20rail)%2C%20resources%2C%20power%20generation%20and%20distribution%2C%20renewable%20energy%2C%20gas%20and%20infrastructure%2C%20agro%20(commodities%2C%20edible%20oil%2C%20food%20products%2C%20cold%20storage%20and%20grain%20silos)%2C%20real%20estate%2C%20public%20transport%20infrastructure%2C%20consumer%20finance%20and%20defence%2C%20and%20other%20sectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739303880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fvhol03do_donald-trump_625x300_12_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-pauses-anti-bribery-law-fcpa-what-it-means-for-adani-group-7689022%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20ordered%20a%20pause%20in%20the%20enforcemen