45a5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222022%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHarley%20Finkelstein%20is%20the%20president%20of%20the%20e-commerce%20platform%20Shopify.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%20for%20The%20Business%20of%20Fashion%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHarley%20Finkelstein%2C%20Shopify's%20president%2C%20said%20the%20company%20supports%20policies%20like%20de%20minimis.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20had%20planned%20to%20eliminate%20the%20de%20minimis%20loophole%20allowing%20duty-free%20shipping.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFinkelstein%20said%20Shopify%20built%20tools%20for%20merchants%20to%20collect%20duties%20at%20checkout.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EShopify%20president%20Harley%20Finkelstein%20spoke%20out%20in%20favor%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshein-temu-wont-be-killed-by-de-minimis-exemption-changes-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ede%20minimis%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20saying%20that%20countries%20should%20make%20it%20easier%20to%20sell%20low-cost%20items%20cross-border.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20executive%20order%20issued%20by%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20on%20February%201%20effectively%20ended%20de%20minimis%2C%20or%20Section%20321%2C%20a%20provision%20of%20US%20customs%20law%20that%20allows%20for%20the%20duty-free%20shipment%20of%20items%20valued%20at%20less%20than%20%24800.%20After%20this%20order%20was%20issued%2C%20e-commerce%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrands-scramble-as-trump-ends-de-minimis-shipments-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebrands%20%E2%80%94%20including%20many%20that%20use%20Shopify%20%E2%80%94%20scrambled%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20adjust%20their%20supply%20chains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20think%20protections%20like%20de%20minimis%20are%20crucial%20for%20small%20businesses%20that%20engage%20in%20trade%2C%26quot%3B%20Finkelstein%20said%20on%20the%20company's%20fourth-quarter%20earnings%20call.%20%26quot%3BBy%20exempting%20these%20low-value%20shipments%20from%20taxes%20and%20duties%2C%20they%20keep%20costs%20down%20and%20allow%20entrepreneurs%2C%20I%20think%2C%20to%20compete%20on%20a%20much%20larger%20scale.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRather%20than%20eliminating%20de%20minimis%2C%20countries%20should%20really%20try%20to%20streamline%20these%20custom%20processes%20and%20improve%20digital%20duty%20collection%20to%20make%20things%20a%20lot%20easier%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinkelstein's%20comments%20came%20in%20response%20to%20a%20question%20from%20Financial%20Technology%20Partners%20analyst%20Craig%20Maurer%20about%20how%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-plan-deadline-trade-policies-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimpending%20tariffs%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20end%20of%20the%20de%20minimis%20exemption%20would%20affect%20Shopify's%20business.%20Shopify%20hosts%20online%20stores%20for%20millions%20of%20sellers%20and%20generates%20revenue%20from%20sales%20transacted%20on%20its%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20paused%20the%20repeal%20of%20Section%20321%20on%20February%207%2C%20giving%20US%20Customs%20and%20Border%20Protection%20more%20time%20to%20implement%20processes%20to%20collect%20duties%20on%20low-value%20packages.%20Canadian%20and%20Mexican%20tariffs%2C%20which%20the%20Trump%20administration%20announced%20on%20February%201%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrudeau-trump-tariffs-canadian-goods-paused-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewere%20also%20postponed%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%2030%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20Finkelstein%20said%20that%20Shopify%20had%20built%20a%20new%20capability%20for%20merchants%20to%20display%20and%20collect%20duties%20at%20checkout.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20customers%20can%20ensure%20they%20shop%20from%20brands%20in%20their%20home%20country%20by%20using%20new%20filters%20on%20the%20Shop%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26