%20its%20IPO%20clients%20to%20have%20at%20least%202%20diverse%20board%20members.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECompany%20reps%20said%20the%20change%20was%20prompted%20by%20a%20legal%20ruling%20over%20Nasdaq's%20board%20diversity%20initiative.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20Tulane%20law%20professor%20questioned%20whether%20the%20Nasdaq%20ruling%20applies%20to%20Goldman%20Sachs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman%20Sachs%20on%20Tuesday%20terminated%20a%20policy%20requiring%20its%20IPO%20clients%20to%20have%20at%20least%20two%20diverse%20board%20members%2C%20citing%20a%20December%20court%20ruling%20over%20a%20similar%20initiative%20at%20the%20Nasdaq%20stock%20exchange.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20result%20of%20legal%20developments%20related%20to%20board%20diversity%20requirements%2C%20we%20ended%20our%20formal%20board%20diversity%20policy%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Goldman%20spokesman%20Tony%20Fratto.%20%26quot%3BWe%20continue%20to%20believe%20that%20successful%20boards%20benefit%20from%20diverse%20backgrounds%20and%20perspectives%2C%20and%20we%20will%20encourage%20them%20to%20take%20this%20approach.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20a%20federal%20appeals%20court%20made%20waves%20when%20it%20struck%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnasdaq-board-diversity-ruling-impact-ipos-goldman-sachs-ilana-wolfe-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edown%20Nasdaq's%20efforts%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20companies%20to%20diversify%20their%20boards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman%20embarked%20on%20a%20legal%20review%20of%20its%20policy%20following%20the%205th%20Circuit%20Court%20of%20Appeals%20decision%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20said.%20As%20the%20review%20was%20taking%20place%2C%20the%20bank%20took%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.goldmansachs.com%2Fdisclaimer%2Fipo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwo%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%20public%20that%20did%20not%20meet%20those%20requirements%3A%20Titan%20America%2C%20a%20company%20that%20provides%20materials%20for%20con