ver%20his%20fitness%20status%2C%20after%20suffering%20a%20back%20injury%2C%20India's%20pace%20spearhead%20has%20been%20finally%20confirmed%20to%20miss%20the%20tournament.%20The%2023-year-old%20pacer%20Harshit%20Rana%20was%20named%20as%20Bumrah's%20replacement%20in%20the%20final%2015-man%20squad.%20In%20another%20selection%20twist%2C%20young%20opener%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20was%20also%20left%20out%20of%20the%20final%20squad%2C%20with%2033-year-old%20mystery%20spinner%20Varun%20Chakaravarthy%20being%20named%20in%20his%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFast%20bowler%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20has%20been%20ruled%20out%20of%20the%202025%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%20due%20to%20a%20lower%20back%20injury.%20The%20Men's%20Selection%20Committee%20has%20named%20Harshit%20Rana%20as%20Bumrah's%20replacement.%20Team%20India%20have%20also%20named%20Varun%20Chakaravarthy%20in%20the%20squad.%20The%20spinner%20will%20replace%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20who%20was%20initially%20named%20in%20the%20provisional%20squad%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BCCI%20said%20in%20a%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20suffered%20a%20back%20injury%20during%20the%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy%2C%20Bumrah%20had%20been%20advised%20five%20weeks%20of%20rest%20as%20confirmed%20by%20chief%20selector%20Ajit%20Agarkar.%20However%2C%20the%2031-year-old%20seamer%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20recover%20in%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPacer%20Harshit%20Rana%20was%20handed%20his%20ODI%20debut%20during%20the%20series%20against%20England%2C%20where%20he%20has%20picked%20up%20four%20wickets%20in%20two%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYashasvi%20Jaiswal%20out%2C%20Varun%20Chakaravarthy%20in%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20big%20change%20to%20India's%20roster%20comes%20in%20the%20form%20of%20opener%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20being%20dropped%20from%20the%20final%20squad%2C%20with%20mystery%20spinner%20Varun%20Chakaravarthy%20taking%20his%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Jaiswal%20and%20Chakaravarthy%20had%20been%20handed%20their%20ODI%20debuts%20during%20the%20series%20against%20England.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChakaravarthy%20forced%20his%20way%20into%20contention%20after%20imperious%20form%20during%20the%20T20I%20series%20against%20England%2C%20where%20he%20picked%20up%2014%20wickets%20in%20five%20games%2C%20being%20named%20the%20'Player%20of%20the%20Series'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaiswal%20was%20India's%20top%20run-scorer%20across%20all%20formats%20in%202024%2C%20but%20has%20only%20played%20one%20ODI%20to%20date%2C%20with%20most%20of%20his%20runs%20coming%20in%20Test%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENon-travelling%20substitutes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeam%20India%20have%20named%20three%20non-travelling%20substitutes%2C%20in%20case%20of%20injury%2C%20in%20the%20form%20of%20Jaiswal%2C%20pacer%20Mohammed%20Siraj%20and%20all-rounder%20Shivam%20Dube.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIndia's%20squad%20for%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%202025%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3ERohit%20Sharma%20(Captain)%2C%20Shubman%20Gill%20(Vice-captain)%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20Shreyas%20Iyer%2C%20KL%20Rahul%20(WK)%2C%20Rishabh%20Pant%20(WK)%2C%20Hardik%20Pandya%2C%20Axar%20Patel%2C%20Washington%20Sundar%2C%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%2C%20Harshit%20Rana%2C%20Mohd.%20Shami%2C%20Arshdeep%20Singh%2C%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%2C%20Varun%20Chakaravarthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENon%20Travelling%20substitutes%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%2C%20Mohammed%20Siraj%20and%20Shivam%20Dube.%20The%20three%20players%20will%20travel%20to%20Dubai%20as%20and%20when%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739297700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F4tet3mlg_jasprit-bumrah_625x300_04_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fjasprit-bumrah-ruled-out-of-indias-champions-trophy-2025-squad-bcci-make-two-big-changes-7688815%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Mens%20Selection%20Committee%20has%20named%20Harshit%20Rana%20as%20Bumrahs%20replacement%22%2C%22autho