rofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20two%20of%20the%20biggest%20players%20in%20Indian%20cricket%20right%20now%2C%20are%20at%20the%20proverbial%20crossroads%20of%20their%20career.%20Their%20class%20is%20unquestionable%20but%20their%20current%20form%20is%20not.%20Both%20the%20senior%20stars%20have%20had%20a%20tumultuous%20run%20after%20the%20T20%20world%20Cup%202024.%20They%20have%20already%20retired%20from%20the%20shortest%20format%20and%20now%20question%20marks%20are%20being%20raised%20on%20whether%20they%20should%20continue%20in%20the%20other%20formats%20too.%20Rohit%20is%20few%20months%20short%20of%2038%2C%20while%20Kohli%20celebrated%20his%2036th%20birthday%20a%20few%20months%20ago.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20failures%20in%20Australia%20and%20against%20New%20Zealand%20in%20Tests%2C%20all%20eyes%20are%20on%20whether%20they%20will%20be%20able%20to%20leave%20a%20mark%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20or%20not.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%201983%20World%20Cup-winning%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Kapil%20Dev%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F40958-ramlal-nikhanj-kapil-dev-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKapil%20Dev%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20it's%20not%20a%20bad%20thing%20to%20talk%20to%20outsiders%20to%20mend%20the%20problems.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20there%20are%20no%20runs%2C%20problems%20are%20on%20all%20sides.%20The%20best%20way%20out%20is%20to%20talk%20to%20cricketers%2C%20who%20are%20your%20'type'.%20See%20you%20old%20videos%20and%20analyse%20how%20you%20used%20to%20play.%20You%20will%20not%20get%20the%20same%2020-25%20year%20old%20Virat%20Kohli%20or%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20but%20if%20you%20see%20your%20old%20videos%2C%20you%20will%20get%20an%20idea.%20Cricket%20is%20a%20game%20of%20confidence.%20Age%20is%20a%20factor%20but%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20they%20have%20forgotten%20to%20play%20the%20game.%20You%20have%20to%20adjust%2C%26quot%3B%20Kapil%20Dev%20said%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%