nology%2Ftech-news%2Fsamsung-galaxy-f06-5g-phone-to-be-launched-on-february-12-what-to-expect-125021101289_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2221%20Tons%2C%2039%20Fifties%2C%207200%20Runs%20Yet%20No%20India%20Debut.%20Ex%20KKR%20Star%20Retires%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EProlific%20Saurashtra%20batter%20Sheldon%20Jackson%20on%20Tuesday%20retired%20from%20professional%20cricket%20after%20a%20career%20spanning%2015%20years%2C%20his%20last%20outing%20ending%20in%20a%20defeat%20to%20Gujarat%20in%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy%20quarterfinal.%20Jackson%2C%2038%2C%20retires%20with%20more%20than%207200%20runs%20in%20105%20first-class%20matches%20with%20a%20highest%20score%20of%20186%2C%2021%20hundreds%20and%2039%20half-centuries.%20That%20he%20ended%20his%20career%20with%20an%20average%20of%20over%2045%20speaks%20volumes%20about%20his%20consistency%20in%20first-class%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJackson%20has%20been%20a%20multidimensional%20cricketer%20and%20besides%20being%20a%20reliable%20batsman%20and%20an%20excellent%20fielder.%20He%20also%20kept%20wickets%20for%20Saurashtra%20in%20the%20limited-over%20competitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20longer%20format%2C%20however%2C%20he%20was%20not%20required%20to%20do%20the%20duty%20thanks%20to%20Sagar%20Jogiyani's%20presence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20scored%2014%20and%2027%20in%20his%20final%20two%20outings%20as%20Gujarat%20won%20by%20an%20innings%20and%2098%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJackson%2C%20who%20was%20once%20part%20of%20the%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20set-up%20after%20being%20spotted%20by%20former%20Bengal%20player%20Joydeep%20Mukherjee%2C%20made%20his%20debut%20for%20Saurashtra%20in%20December%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20being%20on%20the%20fringes%20of%20selection%20for%20his%20state%20team%20Saurashtra%20for%20three%20years%2C%20he%20made%20his%20debut%20in%20December%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20made%20four%20fifties%20and%20three%20hundreds%20in%20