%20three-year%20gap%2C%20which%20raised%20questions%20from%20employers.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20my%20eyebrows%20or%20hair%20back%20at%20that%20time%2C%20so%20people%20were%20naturally%20curious.%20When%20asked%2C%20I%20shared%20my%20cancer%20journey%20honestly%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20his%20openness%2C%20some%20employers%20were%20sceptical%20about%20his%20ability%20to%20handle%20the%20pressures%20of%20a%20corporate%20job.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20employers%20who%20asked%20if%20I%20could%20cope%20with%20corporate%20life%20after%20everything%20I%20had%20been%20through%2C%20and%20some%20even%20turned%20me%20down%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20admits.%20This%20rejection%20led%20to%20a%20sense%20of%20frustration%20but%20also%20inspired%20him%20to%20take%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20%E2%80%98Ride%20of%20Hope%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20decided%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F293230%2Fcancer-survivor-helps-odisha-women-patients-with-free-chemotherapy-treatment%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraise%20awareness%20about%20cancer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20came%20up%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20cancer%20awareness%20ride%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20He%20planned%20to%20travel%20across%20the%20country%2C%20meet%20cancer%20patients%2C%20and%20show%20them%20that%20life%20could%20continue%20after%20chemotherapy.%20However%2C%20he%20needed%20funds%20to%20make%20this%20dream%20a%20reality.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20called%20my%20father%20for%20some%20financial%20support%2C%20and%20my%20brother%20stepped%20in%2